quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  35,15,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe, ko onon woni hatonjim…ďe e Alla …ďen, Alla kan, ko Kanko woni Galo Yettinii…óo On"
  35,16,"Si O yi…óii, O na…ďa on, O adda tagu hesu"
  35,17,∆äum wonaali sattu…óum ka Alla
  35,18,"Wonki ronndotaako doŇčgal wonkii goo. Hay si teddiraaki [junuubi] kin noddii e ronndaneede, ki ronndantaake hay huunde, hay si ko …ďadondiraa…óo Anndu ko jertintaa [nana waaju], ko …ďen huliroo…ďe Joomi mun ka wirnii, …ďe √Īii…ďi e Julde. Kala on la…ď…ďinii…óo, haray ko hoore makko o woni la…ď…ďinanaade. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  35,19,Bun…óo e yi'oowo fotataa
  35,20,wanaa ni…ďe …óen e ndaygu ngun
  35,21,wanaa …óowdi ndin e henndu wulndu ndun
  35,22,"Wanaa kadi wuur…ďe …ďen fotata e maay…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla no nanina on Mo O muuyani. Wanaa an [Nulaa…óo], woni naninoowo, won…ďe ka genaale …ďen"
  35,23,"An a wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo"
  35,24,"Pellet, Men nulirii ma goonga, ko a wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wanaa jertinoowo fe∆ī∆īii e ma…ď…ďe"
  35,25,"Si …ďe fennii ma, hari adinoo…ďe …ďe …ďen fenniino (Nulaa…ďe mun), fewndo …ďen Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe addannoo …ďanngannduyeeji, e ∆äeri e Deftere ndayginoore"
  35,26,Refti nanngitir mi yeddu…ďe …ďen (halakuyee). Taskii no lepte An …óen wa…ótinirnoo
  35,27,"E a tinaali wonnde Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Men fu…óiniri …óam dim…óe seertu…óe noone. Hino ka pelle, …óate daneeje e bo…óeeje seertyu…óe noone, e pete …ďaleeje"
  35,28,"Hino e yim…ďe …ďen, e daabeeji …óin, e neemoraa…ói …óin, …ói nooneeji mun kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko hulata Alla e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, ko anndu…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo, Haforoowo"
  35,29,"∆Āen janngoo…ďe Deftere Alla nden, …ďe √Īii…ďi e julde, …ďe nafqii ko Men arsiki …ďe kon gunndoo e kene, hi…ďe jortii njulaaku ngu sontataa"
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana …ďe njo…ďdiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, O …ďeyda …ďe e …ďural Makko ngal. Kanko, ko O Haforoowo, Annditanoowo [on]"
  35,31,"Kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa e Deftere nden, ko …óum woni goonga, gom…óinde e …óen won…óe yeeso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko Humpitii…óo Rentu…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  35,32,"Refti Men ronini Deftere nden, …ďen …ďe Men su…ďii e jeyaa…ďe Amen. Hino e ma…ď…ďe too√Īu…ďe hoore-mun, hino e ma…ď…ďe hakindin…óo, hino e ma…ď…ďe foolondiroo…ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, duŇčayee Alla; ko …óum woni …ďural mawnungal ngal"
  35,33,"Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …ói naatata e mun, hara hi…ďe cu…óiree ton, jawe kaŇčŇče e kaalise e lu‚Äôu-lu‚Äôu; comci ma…ď…ďe …óin ton, ko sooyi"
  35,34,"∆Āe wi'a: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ittan…óo en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko Haforoowo, Warjotoo…óo"
  35,35,"On weernir…óo en …ďural Makko ngal, e galle √Īii…ďal, tampere (woo) he…ďataa en ton, wanaa ronkere he…ďata en ton"
  35,36,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani …ďen; maayde √Īaawetaake e ma…ď…ďe, sakko …ďe maaya, …ďe hoynantaake kadi lepte magge …óen. Ko wano nii Men yo…ďitirta kala yeddu…óo"
  35,37,"Hara hi…ďe ooloo nder ton […ďe wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, yaltin men; men golla mo∆ī∆īere, hara wonah ko men gollaynoo kon\". [O jaaboo …ďe]: \"E men wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotoo…óo waajitoranoo e mun? Jertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa mee…óee, sabu faabo alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo wirnii…ói kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Ko O Anndu…óo ko suu…óii e …ďer…óe"
  35,39,"Ko Kanko woni wa…óu…óo on lontii…ďe ka leydi. Kala yeddu…óo, ko e makko lorra geddi makko yantata. Yeddugol heefer…ďe …ďen, …ďeydataa …ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa tikkere. Yeddugol …ďeydataa heefer…ďe …ďen, si wanaa hayrere"
  35,40,"Maaku: \"E on yi'ii rendii…ói mon rewoton gaanin Alla …óin? Hollee lam ko …ói tagi ka leydi. Kaa hi…ói mari ge…ďal e [tagugol] kammuuli …óin? Kaa Men addan …ďe Deftere, nde …ďe woni e …ďanndannduyee mun? Si ko woni, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen alaa e fodude yoga ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa hodo"